Class RpcClientEndpoint<A,R,T extends CarriesInvocationId>

  • java.lang.Object

      • org.infogrid.comm.WaitForResponseEndpoint<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the type of the argument of the RPC call
    R - the type of the return value of the RPC call
    T - the message type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageEndpointListener<T>, org.infogrid.util.logging.CanBeDumped

    public abstract class RpcClientEndpoint<A,R,T extends CarriesInvocationId>
extends WaitForResponseEndpoint<T>
    An abstract communications endpoint for Remote-Procedure-Style communications. Subclasses add marshalling and unmarshalling functionality.
